author: arj
msg: Second major checkin of the workflow package. The API is mostly stable,  but it should still be regarded as volatile. Workflow now includes a working user interface (Workflow.jsp). UI has a workflow "inbox" (for decisions a user has been asked to make) and an "outbox" (for workflowsa user has started). Users must be authenticated to see their workflows.

author: arj
msg: 'SaveWikiPageWorkflow' is now operational. It provides moderation for saving wiki pages, and is turned off by default. See jspwiki.properties for configuration guidelines.
